name: Faux Fur Coat
description:
Everyone has been asking about me getting some more faux fur jackets and I've managed to grab this cute one. It's a soft, dark brown jacket that would keep you super warm on those cold days. Would look great with a dress and some cite patterned tights.

Size: 6 - 16
The smaller the size, the baggier it will be.

Condition: Good
Slight tear on the sizing label on the inside of the jacket and a very small hole in one of the pockets.

name: Topshop Horse Jumper
description:
I grabbed this number in a charity shop a while back and thought it would be so cute for goldcrest! This is a cream coloured topshop jumper with a horse print on the front. Would look good with a pair of shorts and knitted knee high socks. 

Size: 6-12
Labelled as a size 12, but if you're wanting it a wee bit baggier it's better to be a smaller size.

Condition: Mint
Almost like it's not warn.

name: 80's Batwing Oversized Jumper
description:
If anyone is into their 80's jumpers, then this is a must in their wardrobe! This is a black and gold batwing jumper that is guaranteed to turn heads and is a perfect piece for everyday wear or as part of an 80's costume. 

Size: 10-18
the smaller your size the baggier the jumper

Condition: Good
Slight wear on the sleeves.

name: 80's New Look Oversized Jumper
description:
Cute oversized jumper with big patterns of cats, rabbits, horses, ducks and other designs all over the jumper. Would be brilliant for those cold months leading up to summer. Would look good with leggings, jeans, shorts with stocking designed tights.

Size: 6-18
The smaller size you are, the baggier the jumper will be.

Condition: Good
No rips, tears but only slight worn on the ends of the sleeves with "bobbles"
